&lt;p&gt;As an Ad Operations Specialist, you will play a key role in supporting Taboola&#39;s global advertising business by ensuring the seamless execution, monitoring, and delivery of digital advertising campaigns. Working closely with Enterprise Account Managers and cross-functional teams, you will help drive campaign success by proactively monitoring performance, identifying issues, preparing insightful reports, and ensuring operational excellence across a high-volume portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires a strong analytical mindset, exceptional attention to detail, and a customer-first approach. You will collaborate with Product, Support, R&amp;amp;D, and Business teams to resolve campaign-related challenges, while becoming a trusted expert in Taboola&#39;s advertising platforms and tools. Success in this role requires curiosity, ownership, adaptability, and the ability to thrive in a fast-paced, dynamic environment.&lt;/p&gt;
