&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Realize your potential by joining the leading performance-driven advertising company and a proud Great Place to Work® Certified employer in Israel.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Advertiser Account Manager in our Tel Aviv Office, you’ll play a vital role in our business and for our clients. You will work closely with top enterprise brands and agencies in the Israeli domestic market to help them reach their business KPIs, identify growth opportunities at scale, and grow revenue for a large book of accounts. &lt;strong&gt;This is a temporary position for a Maternity Leave Replacement.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To thrive in this role, you&#39;ll need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of professional experience (client-facing in the digital media /brand marketing)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mandatory proficiency in both spoken and written Hebrew&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding relationship management and customer service skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical aptitude for managing multiple platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical abilities to draw conclusions from data to enhance performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with performance-driven advertising and campaign optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with the Israeli digital advertising market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How you’ll make an impact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with top enterprise brands and agencies in the IL domestic market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist clients in reaching their business KPIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and pursue opportunities for revenue growth at scale within your book of accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor content and video campaign performance, conducting weekly and quarterly calls to guide clients on strategy and optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product, Marketing, and Support teams to drive revenue and enhance customer satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot and resolve client issues in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Taboola?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you ask Taboolars what they love about working here, they’ll tell you that they’ve been empowered to realize their full potential while growing and learning from and with smart and talented people. They’ll also share more about:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adam Singolda, Taboola Founder and CEO says; “You can copy anything from another business but you can’t copy a company’s culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Well-being: Enjoy comprehensive benefits (health, etc.), a fully stocked kitchen, and location-specific perks (gym partnerships, parking)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility: We offer a hybrid work schedule with 3 days in-office with an option to come in more often if desired.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with some of the biggest names: Our publisher partners include Yahoo, Conde Nast, Fox Sports, NBCU, ESPN, CBS, and E! Online. Our advertiser clients include Wells Fargo, Honda, Pinterest, and Expedia.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
