&lt;p&gt;As Assistant Corporate Controller in our finance &amp;nbsp;group in our Bangalore Office,you’ll be responsible for managing the day-to-day accounting functions, ensuring proper treatment of complex transactions, and supporting the reporting of results across our global offices. The Assistant Corporate Controller will report to the Corporate Finance Director.&lt;/p&gt;
