&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Deep knowledge of US GAAP (specifically ASC 718, 606 and 260) and SEC reporting is essential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global Exposure:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience with off-shore subsidiaries is a must.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Proficiency:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong understanding of US GAAP (specifically ASC 718, 606, and 260) and SEC reporting requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
